{
  "stem": "6989.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 34.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 233,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- but they lived in a little house in Freeport.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 233,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you know, they had a candy store in Freeport.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 234,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, she had a father though.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 235,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She had-- the father was alive, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 236,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she took us there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 237,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were with her, like, for about eight months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 237,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 237,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Greenbergs ?] came to the United States.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 237,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this, her father, arranged for us to have an apartment in the Bronx.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 238,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And by that time, we became sort of a family again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 239,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I entered school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 240,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 241,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did go to-- I graduated high school here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 242,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Actually--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 243,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I was just going to say that my first schooling that I had was, of course, that I told you, the few months--",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 244,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--with Lena.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 244,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, basically, the main thing was really in Bad Reichenhall.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 244,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Which we were there approximately a year.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 245,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Through the Hebrew schools.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 245,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they organize schools there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 246,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I learned a little bit Hebrew and writing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 246,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was my beginning of education.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 247,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- they were through the organizations.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 247,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know whether it was the UJA or--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 248,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or I think HIAS.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 248,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think maybe it was HIAS.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 249,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That-- yeah, one of those.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 250,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Palestinian, I just remember belonging to a group--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 251,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which was Yehud.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 252,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were just, you know, for hiking--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 253,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and singing Hebrew songs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 254,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And trying to entice us to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 255,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which at one time I was considering to run away and go with them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 256,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's what they wanted me to do actually.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 257,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I don't think I had the courage to do that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 258,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I stayed put.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 259,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There, they also-- they gave lessons like--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 260,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--English lessons a little bit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 261,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was very little, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 262,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember speaking-- you know, when I first came, I didn't speak Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
